<div class="app-card-container contact-opacity">
  <div class="card">
    
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="about-pic-height">
          <%= image_tag "blackrocks2.jpg", alt: "Profile Image", class: "profile-image" %>
        </div>

        <hr>

        <h3 id="focus">Areas of Focus</h3>
        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">
              <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
              <div class="progress">
                <div 
                  class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                  role="progressbar"
                  aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                  aria-valuemax="100"
                  style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                ></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="col-md-8">
        <div class="about-description-height">
          <h1>About Me</h1>
          <div class="about-description-text">
            <p class="about-card-top">With over two full weeks of experience in developing web apps, I'm pretty much the greatest choice in the world to build your site. What could go wrong?</p>

            <p class="about-card-bottom">Regardless of my experience level, you can be sure that your site will be put together carefully, thoughtfully and that I'll come up with some cool ideas to make your site standout from your competitors.</p>
          </div>


          <p>
            <button
              class="btn btn-info"
              type="button"
              data-toggle="collapse"
              data-target="#jobHistory"
              aria-expanded="false"
              aria-controls="jobHistory"
            >
              Job History
            </button>

            <button
              class="btn btn-info"
              type="button"
              data-toggle="collapse"
              data-target="#education"
              aria-expanded="false"
              aria-controls="education"
            >
              Education
            </button>
          </p>
        </div>

        <hr>

        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-4">
                <h3 class="about-class-title">Job History</h3>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-8">
                <p>I've been very blessed to work at some great places over the years. Here are some of my favorites.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <hr>

            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <%= image_tag "DSUClimb.png", alt: "DSU Climbing logo", width:"300" %>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <h3 class="about-title">Dixie State University</h3>
                <p class="about-text">Adjunct Professor of Rock Climbing and Mountain Biking</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <hr>

            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <%= image_tag "campsaver.png", alt: "Campsaver logo", width:"300" %>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <h3 class="about-title">Campsaver LLC</h3>
                <p class="about-text">Buyer for Rock Climbing Products for www.campsaver.com</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <hr>

            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <%= image_tag "SEED.png", alt: "SEED logo", width:"300" %>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <h3 class="about-title">USU SEED Program</h3>
                <p class="about-text">Loan Officer and Assistant to the Program Director</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <hr>

            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <%= image_tag "paragon.jpg", alt: "Paragon logo", width:"300" %>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <h3 class="about-title">Paragon Adventures</h3>
                <p class="about-text">Rock Climbing, Mountain Biking, Canyoneering Guide</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <hr>

          </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-4">
                <h3 class="about-class-title">Education</h3>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-8">
                <p>Higher education has been a big and enjoyable part of my adult life. Here are a few of the places I've studied over the past several years.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <hr>

            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <%= image_tag "bottega.png", alt: "Bottega logo" %>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <h3 class="about-title">Bottega Tech</h3>
                <p class="about-text">Full Stack Development Program</p>
                <p class="about-text">February, 2018</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <hr>

            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <%= image_tag "USU.png", alt: "USU logo" %>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <h3 class="about-title">Utah State University</h3>
                <p class="about-text">BS of History and Business</p>
                <p class="about-text">May, 2012</p>
                <p class="about-text">Cumulative GPA 3.86</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <hr>

            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <%= image_tag "DSU.png", alt: "DSU logo" %>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <h3 class="about-title">Dixie State University</h3>
                <p class="about-text">AS of General Education</p>
                <p class="about-text">December, 2008</p>
                <p class="about-text">Cumulative GPA 3.89</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <hr>

          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>